# RawrXD v3.0 - Complete Token Generator Implementation

## Critical Analysis of Current Implementation

The provided `token_generator.cpp` contains **simulated tokenization** with these critical gaps:
- **Hardcoded vocabulary** with only 13 tokens (vs. 32,000+ in production models)
- **Placeholder comment** indicating truncated list (not loaded from file)
- **Simplified BPE** that only checks vocabulary membership (no merge rules)
- **No subword tokenization** (cannot handle unknown words)
- **No real tokenizer file loading** (merges.txt, vocab.json, etc.)
- **No Unicode handling** (fails on non-ASCII)
- **No validation** (crashes on invalid token IDs)
- **No performance optimizations** (linear search, no caching)
- **No error recovery** (fails silently)
- **No thread safety** (race conditions)
- **No logging** (debugging impossible)

---

## Complete Production-Ready Implementation

